Hoʻomākaukau ʻia ka ʻuala ma nā ʻano he nui: ʻili a ʻili paha, piha a ʻokiʻoki paha, me nā mea hoʻonani a i ʻole. ʻO ka mea pono wale nō e pili ana i ka kuke ʻana e pehu i nā granules starch. Hāʻawi ʻia ka hapa nui o nā kīʻaha ʻuala akā ʻai mua ʻia kekahi, a laila lawelawe ʻia ke anu, ʻo ia hoʻi ka salakeke ʻuala a me ka ʻuala ʻuala (crisps) . ʻO nā kīʻaha maʻamau: ʻuala mashed , i hoʻolapalapa mua ʻia (maʻamau i ʻili ʻia), a laila mashed me ka waiū a i ʻole yogurt a me ka pata; ʻuala kālua holoʻokoʻa ; ʻuala i hoʻolapalapa ʻia a i ʻole ka mahu ; ʻuala a i ʻole nā ​​ʻuala paʻi Farani ; ʻoki ʻia i loko o nā pahu a kālua ʻia; scalloped , ʻokiʻoki ʻia, ʻokiʻoki ʻia a palai ʻia (home fries ); ʻoki ʻia i loko o nā ʻāpana liʻiliʻi liʻiliʻi a palai ( hash browns ); ʻoki ʻia a hana ʻia i dumplings , Rösti a i ʻole pancakes ʻuala . ʻAʻole like me nā meaʻai he nui, hiki ke hoʻomoʻa maʻalahi ka ʻuala i loko o ka umu microwave a paʻa mau i ko lākou waiwai waiwai nui, inā ua uhi ʻia lākou i loko o ka wīwī i hoʻoheheʻe ʻia i mea e pale ai i ka puka ʻana o ka wai; ʻO kēia ʻano hana ka meaʻai e like me ka uala mahu, ʻoiai e mau ana ke ʻano o ka ʻuala i kālua ʻia. Hōʻike pinepine ʻia nā ʻuala ma ke ʻano he mea kohu . Hoʻomoʻa ʻia ka ʻuala ma waena o 10 a 25 [90] mau minuke, e like me ka nui a me ke ʻano, e lilo i palupalu.